</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><sp=
an
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Go to Fleet</span></b><span style=3D'mso-no-proo=
f:yes'>:
moves the view to the selected fleet in the main screen<o:p></o:p></span></=
