o-proof:
yes'>: sends all of the ships in the selected fleet to be refueled (and
repaired if damaged) at the nearest refuelling point<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
